AWS::AmazonMQ::ConfigurationAssociation.note: Association via configuration block on Broker

AWS::AppSync::GraphQLSchema.note: Schema provided via graphQLApi schema argument

AWS::FSx::FileSystem.note: Different resources per FSx file system type

AWS::Glue::Partition.note: Use a `#` delimiter between partition values, e.g. `123456789012:MyDatabase:MyTable:val1#val2`

AWS::IAM::UserToGroupAddition.note: to import IAM user group membership using the user name and group names separated by /. For example: `user1/group1/group2`

AWS::MediaConvert::JobTemplate.note: Job templates managed on the queue resource

AWS::MediaConvert::Preset.note: Presets managed on the queue resource

AWS::ServiceCatalog::AcceptedPortfolioSh.note: Import using the portfolio share ID. For example: port-12344321:ACCOUNT:123456789012
